      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like compression though. it feels intentional. like there's this specific low-end rhythm that keeps hitting right when im trying to think clearly. it's almost like they're using the frequencies to mess with my head. if they were using subliminal audio to influence people, how would you even detect it? like what would the signal actually look like?",
